# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Monorepo root ignore. Each package (backend/, frontend/) also keeps
# its own .gitignore; these patterns are defense-in-depth so real
# student PII and secrets can never reach a remote.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/

# Builds
**/dist/

# Environment / secrets
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.bak-*
**/.env.tmp-*
*.enc.json
**/.dev-encryption-key

# Databases — contain real student PII + BYOK keys. NEVER commit.
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
**/data/
**/.db-backups/

# Generated / large artifacts
**/generated/
eng.traineddata

# Logs
*.log
**/logs/

# OS noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
